title: 14a00 - Purpose and use of FOH Chapter 14.
text:
This chapter supplements 29
C.F.R. Part 4, which contains the U.S. Department of Labor’s regulations and
interpretations with respect to the McNamara-O’Hara Service Contract Act of
1965, as amended.
